# Bill of Material
- Rasperry Pi 4 model B, RAM indifferent
- Arduino Uno board, for wireless temperature measurement
- 2 modules nRF24l01
- 2 signal amplifier: adafruit MAX31865
- 2 RTD PT100 temperature sensors: 1 covered with only a thin layer for air temperature measurement, the other one with regular cover to ensure integrity while embedded into concrete
- Relay: solid state relay is preferable
- logic voltage converter 3V - 5V
- LCD screen 4x20
- 4 push buttons
